OL,5,G0900 Bargain Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,6,     FSeries favourite Colin - drag
OL,7,     Fqueen by night, loving husband,
OL,8,     Ffather and animal rescue centre
OL,9,     Fboss by day - with his husband
OL,10,     Frenovate a property on their farm
OL,11,     Ffor the rental market.
OL,12,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,13,     FCatching up with some of the cases
OL,14,     Fin the series, including Les who
OL,15,     Fhad been forced to sleep on his
OL,16,     Fsofa for two months and
OL,17,     F70-year-old Joan whose tenants
OL,18,     Frefused to go quietly.
