OL,5,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FIn Bradford there's a high-octane
OL,7,     Fchase through a housing estate,
OL,8,     Fand Yorkshire's back roads have
OL,9,     Ftheir peace disturbed by two cars
OL,10,     Fcarrying gun-toting drug dealers.
OL,11,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,12,     FA driver nearly causes carnage to
OL,13,     Fmake sure his takeaway stays hot,
OL,14,     Fa large cannabis stash is found at
OL,15,     Fthe scene of a crash, and a drunk
OL,16,     Fdriver gets caught short.
OL,17,G1300 Traffic Cops: Under Attack
OL,18,     FYorkshire's traffic cops are in
OL,19,     Fhot pursuit of some criminals
OL,20,     Fdragging a generator with just one
OL,21,     Fwheel across the county, and a van
OL,22,     Ffull of contraband in Bradford.
OL,23,Vppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
