OL,5,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,6,     FA runaway mugger rams Faulko off
OL,7,     Fthe road and puts him in hospital.
OL,8,     FThe team hunts down the driver
OL,9,     Fresponsible. Meanwhile Liam locks
OL,10,     Fup a rogue biker.
OL,11,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,12,     FSpike breaks out a drug wipe for a
OL,13,     Fteenage tearaway on two wheels,
OL,14,     Fbut will the biker heed his dad's
OL,15,     Fwise words?
OL,16,G1600 Police Interceptors
OL,17,     FChris's tracker dog Ronny has a
OL,18,     Ftwitchy nose but will this canine
OL,19,     Fcrime fighter manage to track down
OL,20,     Fa villain?
