OL,5,G1700 Call the Bailiffs: Time to Pay Up!
OL,6,     FMark and Sam try to recover
OL,7,     F#11,000 from a cleaning business,
OL,8,     FVlad tackles a #6,000 catering
OL,9,     Fdebt, and Alex pursues #55,000 in
OL,10,     Funpaid taxes from a property
OL,11,     Fbuyer.
OL,12,G1800 Home and Away
OL,13,     FJo makes a drunken dial. Eden
OL,14,     Fconfides in Tane. A crime wave
OL,15,     Fhits Summer Bay.
OL,16,G1830 Home and Away
OL,17,     FTane lays down the law. Mackenzie
OL,18,     Fis hurting. Alf and John team up.
OL,19,     FSonny is intrigued by a stranger.
