OL,5,G1900 GPs Behind Closed Doors
OL,6,     FThe GP's at Hall Green Health meet
OL,7,     Fpatients confused by advice given
OL,8,     Ffrom different healthcare
OL,9,     Fprofessionals. Returning patient
OL,10,     FFarheena is back in the surgery.
OL,11,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,12,     FAs a heatwave hits Yorkshire, the
OL,13,     Fpatient numbers rise with the
OL,14,     Ftemperature. Documentary series
OL,15,     Ffilmed inside Barnsley casualty
OL,16,     Fdepartment.
OL,17,G2100 Ambulance: Code Red
OL,18,     FA man is stabbed multiple times,
OL,19,     Frequiring urgent attention and
OL,20,     Ftreatment; a 64-year-old stops
OL,21,     Fbreathing while her husband calls
OL,22,     Fthe hospital.
